    "The goal of TS-CHIEF was to obtain the benefits of multiple representations without the massive processing requirement of the original HIVE-COTE.",
    "The Randomised Interval-Shapelet Transformation (RIST) pipeline is a simpler approach than the previously described hybrids.",
    "Rather than constructing an ensemble, RIST concatenates the output of multiple transformations to form a pipeline classifier.",
    "RIST uses the transformation portions from the interval based DrCIF",
